{"tid":2278903,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登政權熱門防長人選︰美應具備72小時擊沉整支中國海軍能力","createTime":"2020-11-09T12:10:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T17:13:58.000Z","uid":210140,"like":72,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"466dd9b6b322f297c3b2570e46f6a2edcc14d7aa","tid":2278903,"uid":210140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T12:10:20.000Z","msg":"佢同契媽雙劍合璧就正啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3346688?fbclid=IwAR1fimtvJJXJhuEJe-T6wi0IVrcqEsTCdydB7Yw8SVu3q92lUcPH0W_YJh4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3346688%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1fimtvJJXJhuEJe-T6wi0IVrcqEsTCdydB7Yw8SVu3q92lUcPH0W_YJh4&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2BT2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=35558088\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3346688%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1fimtvJJXJhuEJe-T6wi0IVrcqEsTCdydB7Yw8SVu3q92lUcPH0W_YJh4&h=2419d226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3346688?fbclid=IwAR1fimtvJJXJhuEJe-T6wi0IVrcqEsTCdydB7Yw8SVu3q92lUcPH0W_YJh4</a><br />\n<br />\n〔編譯陳成良／綜合報導〕美國民主黨總統候選人拜登競選團隊已在籌備政權交接，各方看好國防部長一職料由歐巴馬任內的國防部政策次長佛洛諾伊（Michele Flournoy）出任，可望成為美國首位女性防長。佛洛諾伊曾暗示，美國應尋求在72小時內，在南海擊沉整支中國海軍的能力，以改變北京風險考量。<br />\n<br />\n佛洛諾伊被視為「自由派中的鷹派」，主張美國應增加軍費維持強盛軍力；她還曾在2015年率其創辦的智庫「新美國安全中心」（CNAS）團隊訪問台灣。<br />\n<br />\n她今年6月18日《外交事務》（Foreign Affairs）期刊網站，發表題為「如何避免亞洲爆發戰爭」的專文，強調美中今日爆發軍事衝突的風險比過去數十年都高，「因為中國軍力增強正削弱美國的威懾力」。<br />\n<br />\n專文表示，有鑑於中國擁有相當的反介入能力，以及能在自家後花園部署比美國更大軍力，美國決策者需要更有「創意」去思考如何改變北京的盤算。<br />\n<br />\n佛洛諾伊直言，假如戰爭爆發，美國目前已不再能夠迅速實現空中、太空或水上水下優勢，美軍在戰場上不管是爭取還是之後保住這些優勢，都要搏鬥，並不斷面臨敵人干擾。她稱這些不確定因素可能會令美國威懾失效，令中國「誤判」，例如封鎖或武統台灣。<br />\n<br />\n她認為，「如果美軍有能力發出可靠的威脅，能在72小時內，擊沉中國在南海的所有軍艦、潛艦以及商船，中國領導人在封鎖或進攻台灣等行動之前就可能會三思而行，他們會需要考慮是否值得將整支艦隊置於風險之中。」<br />\n<br />\n佛洛諾伊被視為熱門防長人選，不過，她曾在歐巴馬執政時期與拜登在埃及和利比亞問題上產生分歧，有可能會遭到共和黨強烈杯葛。<br />\n<br />\n佛洛諾伊主張，美國國防部有必要在與中國的競爭中確保技術、經濟上的優勢，對中國應超越傳統型的軍事應對，例如將武漢肺炎疫情也納入國家安保範圍。"},{"pid":"b2758de0880f589b0d5c48d391af41763ea0cd15","tid":2278903,"uid":248540,"like":34,"dislike":68,"score":-34,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T12:12:27.000Z","msg":"女人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n72小時葬送美國艦隊就有佢份"},{"pid":"89d41290194a9c3e6ef926bd2c5c02f4064fe7d0","tid":2278903,"uid":287422,"like":17,"dislike":3,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T12:13:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n信住一成，等睇賓州變形<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec24c1a02e497ef37d5482447fe5e5114301f54a","tid":2278903,"uid":46388,"like":5,"dislike":16,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T12:13:59.000Z","msg":"叫成班美軍聽個女聲支笛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebf57665c49d853cdf79660047d344ca2981c20e","tid":2278903,"uid":210140,"like":60,"dislike"